Extensis Suitcase Fusion 5

Suitcase Fusion helps you locate and activate fonts only when you need them in order to save valuable system resources and time.

Suitcase Fusion provides auto-activation plug-ins that allow you to automatically activate fonts for documents created in popular design applications, as well as on a system wide level.

With Suitcase Fusion, you'll never need to be concerned that a corrupt font might interrupt your workflow. Potential problems are diagnosed and repairs are automatically applied when a font is added.

Suitcase Fusion is the industrial-strength font management application for all creative professionals. Powered by the Font Management Core, you will always have the font you need when you need it.
